title: read_excel counts hidden sheets.
pid: 9e5f293c-82c7-4539-8f4a-53b3b67851fe
body: |2-
  The Excel file can include hidden sheets.
  If so, what looks like, e.g.,
  the fourth sheet might actually be the sixth.
  This can look like a bug in read_excel, but it isn't.
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
